Title: Relates to determining whether the state can claim federal financial participation for coverage of and payment for certain prescription digital therapeutics
Summary: Directs the department of health to request guidance from the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services to determine whether the state can claim federal financial participation for coverage of and payment for certain prescription digital therapeutics.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to determining whether the state can claim federal financial participation for coverage of and payment for certain prescription digital therapeutics
